About this hotel

Set on a city street, this relaxed hotel is an 11-minute walk from both a marina and Plage municipale beach along the Atlantic Ocean. It's also 2 km from art exhibits at Dar el Makhzen, a former palace, and 14 km from Tangier Ibn Battouta Airport.

Check-in time: 2:00 PM
Check-out time: 1:30 PM

  • Airport shuttle

    About this hotel

    Set on a city street, this relaxed hotel is an 11-minute walk from both a marina and Plage municipale beach along the Atlantic Ocean. It's also 2 km from art exhibits at Dar el Makhzen, a former palace, and 14 km from Tangier Ibn Battouta Airport. …

    Featuring balconies, the simply furnished rooms provide complimentary Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs. Family rooms sleep up to 4 people. Some add ocean views.

    There’s a business center. Parking is available.
